</varlistentry>


<varlistentry>
<term
><synopsis
>void view.setCursorPosition(<parameter
>int <replaceable
>рядок</replaceable
></parameter
>, <parameter
>int <replaceable
>стовпчик</replaceable
></parameter
>);
void view.setCursorPosition(<parameter
>Cursor <replaceable
>курсор</replaceable
></parameter
